<section id="fs-idm61621056" class="critical-thinking">
<title>Critical Thinking Question</title>
<exercise id="fs-idp112946608">
<problem id="fs-idp145420176">
<para id="fs-idp127386256">Suppose Sipho’s town raises the price of bus tickets from R5 to R10 and the price of burgers rises from R20 to R40. Why is the opportunity cost of bus tickets unchanged? Suppose Sipho’s weekly spending money increases from R100 to R200. How is his budget constraint affected from all three changes? Explain.</para></problem>
</exercise>
</section>





